ygData.messageBody:
i don't have any quest items yet. i just made my first trip there. we went
to kill noble dojorn, a _Duel-Wielding_ noble dojorn. definitely the
toughest mob to date i have faced. incredible looking zone though, was glad
i went and look forward to it more when i get some levels =)

Shada Powa, L50 Wood Elf Bard
Tyria Sarkin, L47 High Elf Wizard
<Afterlife> Mithaniel Marr Server
